 Sylvester Oromoni Jr. a late 12-year-old Dowen college student, had his autopsy results released. Tonto Dikeh, a popular Nollywood actress, claimed this and urged the family to make the result public because it is now a public matter. READ ALSO: Sylvester Oromoni: Your Ignorance Does Not Excuse Stupidity – Kemi Olunloyo Slams Falana According to Tonto Dikeh, Nigerians have been fighting for justice, and it is best if the results of the autopsy are made public. She wrote: “Autopsy result for captain Sylvester is out. We would appreciate if it’s made public because this is a public case and we are all his family now. We have/need to know all that can be told. I appreciate how everyone is keeping the spirit with the fight for #justiceforslyvester, It’s truly inspiring… May you never cry and not get help, please don’t stop!! We want TRANSPARENCY” See post below: 